DTDFVocab:inputTo EclipseHonoMiddleware PredictiveAnalyticsService
DTDFVocab:inputTo EclipseDittoMiddleware VirtualToPhysicalControlService
DTDFVocab:inputTo EclipseDittoMiddleware LifecycleManagementService
DTDFVocab:inputTo UnrealEngineVisualization RealTimeMonitoringService
DTDFVocab:inputTo UnrealEngineVisualization StakeholderDashboardService
DTDFVocab:inputTo BimToRuntimeConverter ModelDrivenDeploymentService
DTDFVocab:inputTo EnergyPerformanceModel EnergyOptimizationEnabler
DTDFVocab:inputTo LightingPerformanceModel AdaptiveLightingEnabler
DTDFVocab:inputTo OperationalDataStore PredictiveAnalyticsEnabler
DTDFVocab:inputTo OperationalDataStore VisualizationEnabler
DTDFVocab:inputTo BimRuntimeMetadata MiddlewareIntegrationEnabler
DTDFVocab:inputTo ValidationEnabler ValidationService
DTDFVocab:inputTo PredictiveAnalyticsEnabler PredictiveAnalyticsService
DTDFVocab:inputTo VisualizationEnabler RealTimeMonitoringService
DTDFVocab:inputTo VisualizationEnabler StakeholderDashboardService

